  "title": "Begining Infant Educator | EY 1 / EY 2",
  "description": "<ul><li>Foster a nurturing and welcoming atmosphere where infants can feel safe and secure.</li><li>Embrace the principles of 3Rs (Respect, Reciprocal, Responsive) when interacting with infant.</li><li>Promote age-appropriate and holistic development through engaging and stimulating activities.</li><li>Prioritise the safety and hygiene of all children.</li><li>Enjoy working collaboratively within a team and independently.</li><li>Maintain effective communication with parents and actively engage in parent discussion groups.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Advanced Certificate in Early Years Education or relevant </li><li>Have experience taking care of new born to 18 months old baby</li></ul><p>Check out www.abercare.sg for more details</p><p>Interested applicants may send in your resume to career@abercare.sg</p><p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
